book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.alch: Essence takes up much less space than the item, allowing for easier storage. To brew elixirs, you need to select an essence, and send a redstone signal in. I have found that without it, elixirs will try to brew themselves if possible.
The refined art of making stuff and hoping to not be blown up

Alchemy is similar to brewing in some ways, but is very different overall.
\
\
Blaze powder is needed to fuel alchemy due to burning essence being far too strong, sending glass shards flying everywhere. Placing ingredients into the essence container will turn it into essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.blan: Bland elixirs look like water until you look at the name and effects. Great for those with muscle memory and for worrying your opponents.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.burn: This essence is dangerous to touch, being fire and all.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.butt: Buttered elixirs are much faster to drink, allowing for last second self-buffing.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.clea: Make sure to keep close attention to clear elixirs, as they are completely unidentifiable. Great for parties and roulette.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.cold: Frost forms on the outside of the container, due to tiny droplets of water forming on the surface.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.diff: These diffusing elixirs allow you to remove effects that are ailing you. However, if the effect you have is stronger or longer than what the elixir has, it will only remove the amplifier it has and/or the time it has.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.elix: The elixir is your basic effect giving drink. Similar to regular potions.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.esse: The purest form of things found throughout the world. Their use is important for alchemy, allowing a more controlled approach to creating elixirs than potions have.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.evil: The creatures this essence forms from appear when you do not get enough sleep. Dangerous to obtain, but quite useful.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.fear: Irrational or rational, everyone has fears, just remember that friends & familiars can help you. This essence radiates fear to those around.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.ferm: Fermented essence seems to have the unique ability to switch a potion from being good to bad and vice versa. I believe this process is called reversion if my history books are correct.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.flow: Constantly shifting and moving, it seems to have similar properties to liquid helium, just without the 0Â°K temperature.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.fung: Fungi are important for those who seek to learn about healing. Just don't go taste testing them.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.glow: Glowing essence has the ability to make some elixirs stronger, usually at a cost of time.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.grit: Grit is used to sand things down, but this essence is used to make uninteresting elixirs.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.grow: Both helpful for gardening and for teaching.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.ling: Works like lingering potions, leaving a field of effects that will make combat more complex.
Like the breath it comes from, elixirs made with lingering essence will stay in the world for a bit of time.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.luck: One might say it is statistics, I say no
It is quite improbable that you will ever have too much luck essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.magm: Magma usually is obtained by magma cubes, but it can also be ejected from the earth as lava.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.midn: Used in making buttered elixirs. The darkest point of the night, it is also good for sky gazing.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.name: Alchemy
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.neth: The most important essence you will probably need. Most of the basic elixirs, known as Vanilla, use this essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.old_: Feelings of nostalgia radiate off of this essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.peac: Finding oneself might need peace, but making clear elixirs requires it.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.powe: Imbuing select elixirs with power essence allows for the effects to last longer.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.rage: What truly is angering is that this essence is used to make bland elixirs.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.reso: This essence is good at picking up sounds at specific frequencies. Keep it away from christmas music or you will forever hear jingle bells.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.rich: Golden carrots are a great food item, which translates in some way to this essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.sad_: While sadness is often seen as a negative thing, it can help make the good moments in life feel all the more better. This essence embodies that.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.shar: Pufferfish are deadly to eat, but are great for sharpness essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.shin: A giant crab comes to mind with this essence.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.sile: *Watch out for wardens when collecting resources for this essence. Bring wool and silk touch.*
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.slim: Made with glue, borax, and glitter.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.slur: Slurry is found in rock tumbling, and is a mixture of water, grit, and the remains of the rocks you tumbled. Make sure to have bath cycles for the rocks to be shiny.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.soul: Souls seemingly burn blue, meaning that the fire is much hotter than normal flames.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.spla: Splash elixirs allow you to throw elixirs, allowing for you to figh enemies and buff allies.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.spre: The explosive force of this essence turns elixirs to splash elixirs, making them a formidable weapon or tool.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.stic: There are several versions of spider silk, with each one having a different purpose. This essence mostly has traits of the variant used for catching prey.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.stur: Some turtle shells are a geometric shape called a gÃ¶mbÃ¶c, with only one stable & one unstable point of rest. I do not think the turtle scutes that form this essence have shells like that.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.swee: Sugar is a great baking ingredient, and this essence is great for elixirs. In neither case is it good for your teeth.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.time: Time is relative, or is it? Yes with this essence around, you just can't control it.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.toka: These lizards are very loud and get their namesake from the 'tokay' sound they make.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.unin: Uninteresting elixirs only have the color to be identified by.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.warp: This essence takes on traits of the fruit that makes it and other ender creatures.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.wate: It would make more sense to directly use water to make essence, but ice is more controllable. Besides, the water container would get consumed as well.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.alchemy.youn: Life begins anew constantly, and this essence seems to be in a perpetual state of said beginning.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.effects.abso: This effect scares creepers away and causes phantoms to ignore you.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.effects.liza: Forces those who are affect to crawl. Useful for vein mining and preventing enemies from running.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.effects.name: Effects
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.effects.vuln: Causes defense to weaken. This is the opposite of Resistance.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.enchantments: Where would we be without enchantments? Probably stuck mining deepslate for the rest of time. The enchantments seen in this tome can help you on your travels, or when fighting others if you like.
Fishing rods can only handle up to Fast Reel III, any more and the rod combusts. Hair can become singed.
A way to use physics to your advantage
This enchantment is placed on your fishing rod, increasing the speed the bobber moves. Great for moving creatures, but makes fishing harder. Pair with grapple for some *reel* fun.
While there are 5 variants of gecko's found in the overworld, there is a secret 6th variant that is only found with commands! I think it has something to do with the number **15**? Idk, but it is *time* to go.
This is a section that gives some info on the entities of the mod.

Early on, fear essence was going to be used to make uninteresting elixirs, before it became a separate item. When adding all the essences, I completely forgot to add fear essence. I had glossed over it on the list. Ironic isn't it?
This is a section that gives some info on essences added.

If you entered here, I am guessing you want to know some stuff that kinda is not lore friendly. You asked for it.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.general.intr: Greetings! I am Geko, the writer of this tome you are holding. You may have borrowed it at your local library, bound a book with scales of your pet geckos, or was gifted it and are giving it a read before it ends on a shelf to never be touched again.
However you got a hold of it does not matter, what matter is *what* you do now.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.general.name: General
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.general.vers:
[Lizard Brain](entry://effects/lizard_brain) and [Absolutely Not](entry://effects/absolutely_not) are able to be brewed in both the brewing stand and the alchemy stand.
\
\
[Vulnerability](entry://effects/vulnerability) cannot be brewed but can be looted.

The first version of the tome! Here is what is introduced in this version:
\
\
[Alchemy](category://alchemy) is an art similar to brewing, but with multiple interesting changes.
\
\
[Fast Reel](entry://enchantments/fast_reel) is applied to the fishing rod, and is good for travel, transport, and pvp.
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.name: Scaled Tome
book.gekosmagic.scaled_tome.tooltip: A guide of the magical world around you.
effect.gekosmagic.absolutely_not.descrip: Scares creepers away and phantoms ignore you.
effect.gekosmagic.vulnerability.descript: Damage dealt to effected entities gains an additional 15% per level.
enchantment.gekosmagic.fast_reel.descrip: Increases the velocity of the fishing bobber.
